		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">EmuandCo wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">magno. Can I open a ROM file and it loads the text out of this ROM or is it just a importer?</div>
<br />
<br />None of both <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /> It is an MSDos program that loads a lot of files (some containing text, others graphics and a few tables and such), encodes it all and inserts it into a fresh new copy of the original ROM. It is somehow like an "importer".

		

