	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No, I'm not disapeared, just too busy!
<br />
<br />That tool doesn't work as you nay think: it is a executable that reads some configuration files, ASM hacks, graphic and text in each bank to compress all together into the ROM file. You can't choose what to update (like the intro screen) but you have to configure some parameters in order to make it work properly.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


